text: We stayed at Sue's condo over Memorial Day weekend and couldn't have had a better time. She was very accommodating to all our needs and did everything she could to make us feel welcome, and I couldn't have been happier with the arrangements. The location is ideal, as it's an easy walk to East Sixth, Downtown, as well as several other bar and restaurant districts in Austin.
title: Chic downtown 6th St. Condo
